                <h4 data-uuid="3ed52d9bfb9b40c8bc459fce4e120440">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="14333372f2344dd4b35c1c35fdd261c1">Hamilton tackled the problem of settling national
                    and state debt.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="a878e60683a54ca1a6873ad91f10e7d6">Settling the Debt</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="fb950497f4044adc82f8e6a3c8aebb44"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section class="graphic-organizer-prompt " data-uuid="80f979682c064e0ca12fffec77c2ff7c">
