            <h5 class="column-head feature" data-uuid="cfc09d3f464045ee8fa1c5d7f3c1efba">Tackling the Debt&#160;</h5>
            <p class="intro-feature" data-uuid="7e426ead25164ee49fc005182be98b60">Following the Revolutionary War, the United States was more than $87 million in debt. Alexander Hamilton
                developed a three-point plan to solve the nation's financial problems.&#160;</p>
            <article class="column-container" data-uuid="bcef32bac541417189cfda5eb6184df4">
                <table class="tabular-list fixed-width less-space-above" data-uuid="38693d64d789442083bec5c4ebe786a3">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="column " data-uuid="5eb461b2e446496f8764457ea40cc42a">Hamilton's Economic Plan</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="head" data-uuid="3795dd8c4fa34586997e85b82b91195c">
                                1. Deal with the Debt
                                <ul data-uuid="45624c1c35e749cc9acb1f6f6ef7e5ea">
                                    <li class="indent" data-uuid="68a438562ae24442b041f454f7c62822">Take on the foreign and domestic debt by replacing creditors' old, low-value bonds with new interest-bearing bonds</li>
                                    <li class="indent" data-uuid="45d940bf32bc4bcb9d221fadb5ac7b83">Take over most of the states' $25 million war debts</li>
                                </ul>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td data-uuid="84bea3c681ef438784cd1ff6f1b328cf"><b>2.</b> <b>Gain Revenue</b><br />
                                <ul data-uuid="b2386f8832ca4572a1e6eb968e37110e">
                                    <li class="indent" data-uuid="cea92d88479042138822ea805762c79c">Pass a tariff to both bring in revenue and help American manufacturers<br />
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td data-uuid="a97799003b5b4ebc8933f9f405444e3d"><b>
                                3. Stabilize the Banking System</b><br />
                                <ul data-uuid="33aa0d27389241d392c9eb08b1ad5c40">
                                    <li class="indent" data-uuid="917eb337b16a4b18b27eff30a3c680e7">Create a national bank<br />
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="indent" data-uuid="dc462a07d79147c0af7bba349af913dd">Create a national mint<br />
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <ol data-uuid="9e79eac6b48946888042acd0b7b7e517">
                                </ol>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
